    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现可免费游玩前两个案件！<br>（主游戏中的所有案件均可直播）</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/872ef6baf9ff43413489bc0627b087f4.webp?t=1763696817\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><strong>《Staffer Case - 异能缉凶》</strong>是一款别具一格的悬疑游戏。玩家需要寻找蛛丝马迹整理成文档，并指出它们之间的矛盾，揭开一系列凶案背后的真相。<br><br>故事发生在经过虚构的1960年代。<br>彼时的伦敦城里罪案频发，原因要归结于有十分之一的人口是超能力者（别称<strong>异能者</strong>）。<br><br>玩家将作为<strong>法力事件专案组</strong>的新人警探<strong>诺特里克</strong>侦破谜案。但光凭普通的调查手段不足以识破超能力案件中的诡计，还需要参考与嫌疑人技能相关的文档拨开迷雾。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/0265d6ab6ff87c7c91559142c5727663.webp?t=1763696817\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/7a38896e717391351d2086984421c92f.poster.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/7a38896e717391351d2086984421c92f.webm?t=1763696817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/7a38896e717391351d2086984421c92f.mp4?t=1763696817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>好在超能力者不只有罪犯，还有法力事件专案组的警探（新人诺特里克除外）！资深警探利用超能力调查案发现场，将发现整理成文档。记有情绪波动的供述、隐藏的痕迹和具体留下时间、乃至残留在物品上的记忆——在这众多线索中找出矛盾吧！<br><br>破解重重谜团，逐步揭开真相！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/dc2061ab7b205da339f504d1ce44d42e.webp?t=1763696817\" width=616 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解决五起超能力案件！<br>游玩两段揭示角色背景和个性的分支故事！</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/5e9aec2552af29693b9ad9704a24add9.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=186 /></span><br><strong>[Case.1：舞台幕后]</strong><br>诺特里克是小镇侦探社的助理，收到了法力现象管理局的来信而前往伦敦。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/f97dceadbb2abd0011f91cf09056b571.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=186 /></span><br><strong>[Case.2：宠物店]</strong><br>超生物：法力现象的突变结果。超生物饲养设施发生了一起事件。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/66ab4f9fe1cc37448dc1f565170eb3a5.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=186 /></span><br><strong>[Case.3：巫师的房间]</strong><br>异能体：具有神秘力量的工具。有人发现了某位著名的异能体收藏家的尸体——被纵向切成两半。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/e42dae128d364ae3db584a4124db6f19.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=186 /></span><br><strong>[Case.4：槲寄生]</strong><br>奥本海默：危险性堪比原子弹的危险级别，无比强大的法力现象。管理局地下的某个设施是专门的收容区。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/ff9fb502d07f5dd9236a150011aeee8b.poster.avif?t=1763696817\" width=620 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/ff9fb502d07f5dd9236a150011aeee8b.webm?t=1763696817\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128480/extras/ff9fb502d07f5dd9236a150011aeee8b.mp4?t=1763696817\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>[Case.5：???]</strong><br>现在和过去的事件，以及藏在背后的真相……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[游戏直播指引]</h2><strong>《Staffer Case - 异能缉凶》可用于免费直播，无时长限制，只要不包含以下内容：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过逆向工程、黑客攻击等方式修改游戏代码或改变游戏内容<br></li><li>歪曲故事主线或聚焦于血腥和成人内容以损害游戏本质的策划<br></li><li>没